el":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:api-test","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131199486,"sessionId":"b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":13326,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"killed","startedAt":1776130995085,"endedAt":1776131198083,"runtimeMs":120587,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":true,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776131194520,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"9285c51d","seq":19}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776117647627,"sessionId":"ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":17388,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context to compose the daily briefing. Let me craft a clean status report for the Telegram group -5212380728.\n\nKey info:\n- Yesterday (2026-04-12): AHV Works review complete, session crash and recovery, BE behind 11 commits, FE synced\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\n\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":177611767